title.narrative: Southern Africa Trade and Transport Facilitation Project

description.narrative: The project development objective of the Southern Africa Trade and Transport Facilitation Program - Phase 1 (APL-1) is to facilitate the movement of goods and people along the Dar Corridor in Tanzania, whilst supporting improvements in the services for HIV/AIDS and road safety. The objective of the Southern Africa Trade and Transport Facilitation Program is to facilitate the movement of goods and people along the north-south corridor (NSC), whilst supporting improvement in the services for Human Immunodeficiency Virus/Acquired Immunodeficiency Syndrome (HIV/AIDS) and road safety.
